article.headline: Mississippi Valley St. 64, Texas Southern 54
article.story: ITTA BENA, Miss. (AP) -- Stanford Speech scored 18 points and Mississippi Valley State beat Texas Southern 64-54 on Monday night. The Delta Devils (8-11, 5-2 Southwestern Athletic Conference) also got 14 points from Richard Cannon, who hit four of his team's eight 3-point field goals, and 10 points from Jefferey Price. Jacques Jones led Texas Southern (9-9, 5-2) with 11 points, while Christopher Moore and Leonta Matthews scored 10 apiece. Mississippi Valley State had a comfortable 38-23 lead at halftime. The Delta Devils held the Tigers to one assist.
